Class ModbusDeviceImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
      • org.eclipse.scada.configuration.modbus.impl.ModbusDeviceImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Device, ModbusDevice, Documentable

    public class ModbusDeviceImpl
extends MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
implements ModbusDevice
    An implementation of the model object 'Device'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Short Description
    • Name
    • Node
    • Port
    • Protocol Type
    • Inter Frame Delay
    • Slaves
    • Type System
